    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As a virgin have I been betrothed to You;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How can I still choose to be tainted by this world?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Purchased with precious blood, I belong to You."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No longer my own, I am fully Yours."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So make me to be precious"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And lovely in Your eyes,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be a virgin chaste and pure,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By Spirit beautified."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Out of my love, I choose"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To keep myself for You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My Beloved, dear Bridegroom."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "These last days, there is much You desire to do,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But first You need some faithful ones to intercede."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just to those who have ceased seeking their own things"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You would nothing hide but would freely speak."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So make me to be precious"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And intimate with You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To be Your close companion, Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your interests, all I view."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, as I’m lingering,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Speak face to face with me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dearest Lord, I am listening."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As this age darker grows, still the cry sounds out:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Redeem the time and pay the price to buy the oil.”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No more days can I waste if I want to hear"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The call, “Enter into your Master’s joy.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So make me to be precious"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And one You’d steal away,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By loving Your appearing,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Expecting You each day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There’s no more time to waste!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your coming, I await!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dearest Jesus, oh, come! Make haste!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    }
